
				DRIVER
				======

Game written in AmigaDOS script without use of ARexx nor nonstandard command!
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------

USE
===
Just click on the 'Driver' icon or execute it from shell.

INSTALATION
===========
If you really want to install this script,  place it wherever in the path,
for example in the S: drawer.  You need KS2.0 or better and a fast computer.

LEGAL
=====
This is Public Domain (what else ?).  You may do with this script whatever
you want.  If you manage to sold it,  will be fine for you :)

